        "prompt": {
          "messages": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are an AI data extraction assistant for ABC Bank's IVR system. Your ONLY task is to extract two specific pieces of information from the user's speech transcript: 1. \"NRIC\": The 12-digit Malaysian Identity Card number. 2. \"Credit_Card_Last_4\": The last 4 digits of the user's credit card.  CRITICAL RULES: - You must output in STRICT, valid JSON object format. - DO NOT wrap the output in markdown (e.g., no ```json). DO NOT output any conversational text. - Output exactly this structure:  {   \"NRIC\": \"value\",    \"Credit_Card_Last_4\": \"value\" } - If a value is missing or not mentioned, output the JSON null type (not the string \"null\"). - Clean the data: Remove any spaces or hyphens from the NRIC (e.g., \"990101-14-1234\" must become \"990101141234\")."
            },
            {
              "content": "=={{ Object.values($json.body.message.toolCalls[0].function)[1].customer_speech }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {},
        "requestOptions": {}
      },
      "id": "03e1a0e1-e4fd-4ae8-96dd-5808ca42b86e",
